OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFamilies face debt squeeze 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fas prices keep rising      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A resurgence in cases of people unable 
OL,6, to cover their debt repayments is      
OL,7, expected, a charity has warned, as the 
OL,8, cost of living hits family budgets.    
OL,10,FDebt advisers are urging people who are
OL,11,Fstruggling with existing debts to come 
OL,12,Fto fresh arrangements on how much to   
OL,13,Frepay each month.                      
OL,15,FDoing so made the basics affordable    
OL,16,Fagain, one dad told the BBC.           
OL,18,FPrices are rising at the fastest rate  
OL,19,Ffor 30 years, creating fresh strain on 
OL,20,Fpeople's finances.                     
